    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/5c5babce3cbbfec2143d7f1d492de769.avif?t=1772213914\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buggy is a cute <strong>bug-collection game</strong>. Play as Fenny to catch bugs around Critter Island, fill your collection book, customize your character, and hang out with friends!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CATCH THEM ALL!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bees, Isopods, Butterflies, Moths and more! There are <strong>over 50 Bugs</strong> you can catch across Critter Island. Complete your <strong>Insectarium</strong>, set bugs free to earn money, unlock customization and receive special rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/d19d0453bd2a0f151230ea99531202a1.poster.avif?t=1772213914\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/d19d0453bd2a0f151230ea99531202a1.webm?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/d19d0453bd2a0f151230ea99531202a1.mp4?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLAY TOGETHER WITH YOUR FRIENDS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buggy is a social space where you can meet new peeps, catch bugs together, goob around and explore Critter Island together. Play with <strong>up to 16 players</strong> together in a single lobby!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/1924db956914828e165a3c3c99468338.poster.avif?t=1772213914\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/1924db956914828e165a3c3c99468338.webm?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/1924db956914828e165a3c3c99468338.mp4?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>UPGRADE YOUR BUG NET!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your strength and stamina, or upgrade your bug net with unique perks to become the legendary bug hunter!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/a45727f8a0abf49ff650a609e6853b5c.poster.avif?t=1772213914\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/a45727f8a0abf49ff650a609e6853b5c.webm?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/a45727f8a0abf49ff650a609e6853b5c.mp4?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOMIZE FENNY!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show your personality with tons of different cosmetics and accessories! Be your own Fenny!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/c7db76f32576582f0d955f637dc571e3.poster.avif?t=1772213914\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/c7db76f32576582f0d955f637dc571e3.webm?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315390/extras/c7db76f32576582f0d955f637dc571e3.mp4?t=1772213914\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
